&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and process bi-weekly payroll for all employees, ensuring accuracy and timeliness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain payroll records, including earnings, deductions, and benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with federal, state, and local payroll regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconcile payroll reports and resolve discrepancies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with HR on new hires, terminations, and compensation changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and distribute payroll reports to Accounting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
